{"tid":826742,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「我的內心太污穢」　新幹線海報歪樓變大鵰","createTime":"2018-09-18T12:31:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T03:52:21.000Z","uid":122,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"abcee3a5737bcbabebb7400fd6b31d2b67a39d78","tid":826742,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:31:40.000Z","msg":"是車窗還是陰莖？日本網友@jisaker_skyrim日前在推特分享一張新幹線N700系列列車的海報，但海報上竟然像畫著一根陰莖，他自嘲「我的內心好像太污穢了」，結果引發巨大迴響，許多人看到的也像他一樣，覺得實在太像陰莖了，甚至有人還熱心地標記起各部位的名稱。<br />\n<br />\n其實讓@jisaker_skyrim誤會的圖片，疑似被改過顏色，有網友發現原始海報上新幹線的車窗其實是用黑框和藍灰色構成，而不是@jisaker_skyrim分享的粉橘色，不過在@jisaker_skyrim搶先引導之下，眾多網友其實就算看了原圖還是忍不住會想歪。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_2005fda6e56e422f7d38767a52d631c4.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180918%2F640_2005fda6e56e422f7d38767a52d631c4.jpg&d=d7Rm0k2e6ZO%2FYWbVS6sc9Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4d50b9b0\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_2005fda6e56e422f7d38767a52d631c4.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"70f4b924a069cb5aa8e211847627f04fbe6b9743","tid":826742,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_ca2f44250580d7c3bcadaa4506727565.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180918%2F640_ca2f44250580d7c3bcadaa4506727565.jpg&d=d7Rm0k2e6ZO%2FYWbVS6sc9Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ce63e4c3\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_ca2f44250580d7c3bcadaa4506727565.jpg</a><br />\n有網友發現原始海報其實並不是粉橘色。翻攝自@jisaker_skyrim的推特<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_531edfa10e10952a070048ff1189f674.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180918%2F640_531edfa10e10952a070048ff1189f674.jpg&d=d7Rm0k2e6ZO%2FYWbVS6sc9Y9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=ceecee1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180918/640_531edfa10e10952a070048ff1189f674.jpg</a><br />\n引發誤會的圖案，其實是駕駛座前方窗戶（紅框處）。翻攝自@z6wCC3Bg3leN2CP的推特"},{"pid":"0ad33d0f0da7af3b33df800f43f2fb4c06434427","tid":826742,"uid":54031,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:34:34.000Z","msg":"Cant see shit"},{"pid":"51ea16e5c498317077da248b24efb68203582f8b","tid":826742,"uid":52942,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:36:46.000Z","msg":"返唔到轉頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b7de35de606e086a8efa9b32c4de94a5db18e2","tid":826742,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:38:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7888484c2202c6dd667e16a8397d5e574ad31c6a","tid":826742,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:38:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"58b3848e4015b245c79b3312d0e9f2827c34981b","tid":826742,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:39:31.000Z","msg":"唔係畫緊賓周咩?"},{"pid":"83fb143dd7d15f25a58b68f4bc55abfbd6ca1595","tid":826742,"uid":9726,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:40:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f0b0610b1524e78702fd3e79a61998cf56d76dec","tid":826742,"uid":25138,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T12:45:00.000Z","msg":"睇完第一張之後<br />\n開第二張睇左勁耐都諗唔明關新幹線咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇埋下面留言同望多幾次先發現到架新幹線<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07a8f890512ad